y.io.graphml.input
Interface ParseEventHandler

public interface ParseEventHandler

The interface of the event listener registration class that is used by the GraphMLParseContext.getParseEvents() property.

This interface allows to register listeners for the ParseEvent, allowing to react to various event during the parse process.

See Also:
ParseEventListener, GraphMLParseContext.getParseEvents(), GraphMLParser
